::DarkMouse::


She looked at her rat.  She decided to call the rat Akura.
"Well Akura, it's another day at the office. The boss is yelling 
about something.  Bots are running about doing the Matrix knows what. 
At least I have you, my new found friend.  And just as soon as the 
boss bot and his group leave the work shop, I can build you a nice 
cage." She sat there holding Akura in her hands nuzzling the little 
rat.
